        <!-- General / Pricing -->
        <div class="faq-item" data-category="general locations">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-1">
            Do Mellow Mushroom prices vary by location?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-1">
            <p>Yes. Because most locations are independently owned franchises, menu prices can differ by 10–25% or more depending on local rent, labor, and ingredient costs. A large specialty pizza might cost $24 in one suburb and $29 in a downtown area. Always check the online menu for your specific address or call the restaurant for current pricing before ordering.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Menu / Pricing -->
        <div class="faq-item" data-category="menu general">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-2">
            What is the typical price for a large pizza at Mellow Mushroom?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-2">
            <p>Based on recent diner reports from 2025–2026, most large (16-inch) specialty pizzas fall in the $24–$32 range before tax. Simpler or build-your-own options often start lower, around $22–$27. Prices fluctuate by location and toppings, so treat these as estimates only and verify locally.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Delivery -->
        <div class="faq-item" data-category="delivery ordering">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-3">
            How much does delivery cost from Mellow Mushroom?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-3">
            <p>Delivery fees usually range from $5–$8 through the restaurant’s own system or $6–$12+ via third-party apps, plus service fees and tip. The base menu prices are generally the same as dine-in, but the total can increase 20–40% with fees. Pickup is often the cheapest option if you want to avoid extra charges.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Locations -->
        <div class="faq-item" data-category="locations general">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-4">
            How do I find the nearest Mellow Mushroom location?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-4">
            <p>Use the official Mellow Mushroom website or app and enter your zip code. The site will show nearby restaurants, hours, and the ability to view that location’s specific menu and prices. This independent guide does not list or update individual store addresses or phone numbers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Rewards -->
        <div class="faq-item" data-category="rewards general">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-5">
            Does Mellow Mushroom have a rewards or loyalty program?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-5">
            <p>Many locations participate in a rewards program where you earn points on purchases that can be redeemed for food or discounts. Details and earning rates can vary by franchise. Check the official app or ask your local store when ordering to see if points are available at that location.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Rewards / Payment -->
        <div class="faq-item" data-category="rewards payment general">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-6">
            Are there coupons or discounts available for Mellow Mushroom?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-6">
            <p>Occasional promotions, happy hour deals on appetizers and drinks, and family meal bundles appear at many locations. Coupons from the official website or app are sometimes accepted. Availability changes frequently and differs by store, so check directly with your local Mellow Mushroom or their online ordering page for current offers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Nutrition / Menu -->
        <div class="faq-item" data-category="nutrition menu">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-7">
            Is the gluten-free pizza at Mellow Mushroom safe for celiacs?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-7">
            <p>Mellow Mushroom offers a certified gluten-free crust at most locations, but cross-contamination is possible in a shared kitchen. Guests with celiac disease or strong sensitivities should speak with staff about preparation and decide their personal comfort level. The crust usually adds a few dollars to the pizza price.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Nutrition / Menu -->
        <div class="faq-item" data-category="nutrition menu">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-8">
            What vegan options does Mellow Mushroom have?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-8">
            <p>Several pizzas can be made vegan by omitting cheese or using plant-based alternatives where available, along with salads and some appetizers. Vegan cheese is not standard at every location. Ask your server or check the online menu for that specific store, as options and pricing can vary.</p>
          </div>
