            Does Mellow Mushroom offer catering for large groups or parties?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-9">
            <p>Yes. Most locations provide catering with pizza party packs, wing platters, salads, and dessert options. Minimums and pricing depend on the store and group size. Contact the catering department at your local restaurant for quotes, lead times, and delivery availability. This guide offers general estimates only.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Ordering / Delivery -->
        <div class="faq-item" data-category="ordering delivery">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-10">
            Can I order Mellow Mushroom online for pickup or delivery?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-10">
            <p>Yes. Online ordering is available through the official Mellow Mushroom website and app, as well as some third-party delivery platforms. Select your location first to see that store’s current menu and prices. Online orders often allow easier customization and sometimes show location-specific deals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

