          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-11">
            Does Mellow Mushroom sell or accept gift cards?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-11">
            <p>Many locations sell and accept gift cards. Availability and redemption policies can differ by franchise. Check with your local store or the official website for current gift card options and balances.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Payment -->
        <div class="faq-item" data-category="payment">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-12">
            What payment methods does Mellow Mushroom accept?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-12">
            <p>Most locations accept major credit and debit cards, cash, and mobile payments. Some also accept gift cards. Policies vary slightly by store, especially for large orders or catering. Confirm accepted methods when placing your order.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Rewards -->
        <div class="faq-item" data-category="rewards">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-13">
            How do Mellow Mushroom rewards points work?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-13">
            <p>Points are typically earned on eligible purchases and can be redeemed for menu items or discounts at participating locations. Earning rates, redemption values, and expiration policies may differ by franchise. Ask your local store or check the app for exact details that apply to you.</p>
