          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-14">
            <p>Hours on holidays such as Thanksgiving, Christmas, and New Year’s vary significantly by location. Some stores close entirely while others have reduced hours. Always check the specific restaurant’s page on the official website or call ahead rather than assuming standard hours.</p>
          </div>
