        <!-- General / Ordering -->
        <div class="faq-item" data-category="general ordering">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-15">
            Does Mellow Mushroom take reservations?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-15">
            <p>Most Mellow Mushroom locations operate on a first-come, first-served basis and do not accept reservations for regular dining. Larger groups or private events may be accommodated through catering arrangements. Call your local store to discuss options for bigger parties.</p>
