          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-17">
            What is on the Mellow Mushroom kids menu and how much does it cost?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-17">
            <p>The kids menu usually includes smaller pizzas, chicken tenders, mac and cheese, or simple salads priced roughly $7–$10. Portions are sized for children and often come with a drink option. Prices and exact items can vary by location.</p>
