        <!-- Menu / Ordering -->
        <div class="faq-item" data-category="menu ordering">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-18">
            How customizable are pizzas at Mellow Mushroom?
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-18">
            <p>You can build your own pizza from the crust up or modify most specialty pies. Choose crust type, sauce, cheese, and any combination of toppings. There is usually a small upcharge for premium or extra toppings. Staff are generally helpful with special requests.</p>
          </div>
